# THE SPONGE · THE SPONGE · LIFE SCIENCE · the animal that is all body · UD0 / life-science

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

![silicon badge of THE SPONGE](the-sponge.silicon.png)
